{
  "stem": "7358.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, uh-- so my feet were beginning to hurt me badly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were beginning to get frostbitten.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was really nothing I could do because the people that had the huts with the heat would not let me stay with them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I just-- gradually, my condition became worse and worse to the point where I no longer was able-- I had such pain that I could not walk much.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And at just about that time, we were in a very large forest.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was sort of like, a road dividing the forest in half.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Not a paved road, but nevertheless, it was a road.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And on the other side of the road, there was another group of Jewish people hiding also-- perhaps 35 of them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And suddenly, we got news that during the morning hours, the Ukrainians attacked that little area there, and they slaughtered most of the people there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Maybe one or two people escaped.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And one guy that escaped knew that we were on this side of the road, deep in the woods, and he came to tell us.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He came to look for shelter, to be with people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he told us what happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the people that- those people, the 40 people that we were close to got very concerned that they would be next.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And in the general area, as I explained to you before, most of the villages were Ukrainian, and there were Polish settlements like, between them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was a river.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The name of the river was the River Sluch.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it was a big river.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
